Class DifferentialEvolution

  • java.lang.Object
    • Catalano.Genetic.Optimization.DifferentialEvolution
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IOptimization

    public class DifferentialEvolution
extends java.lang.Object
implements IOptimization
    Differential Evolution (DE). Differential evolution (DE) is a method that optimizes a problem by iteratively trying to improve a candidate solution with regard to a given measure of quality.
